  npcName: Fine Artiste
  npcPortrait: {fileID: 0}
  dialogueLines:
  - Hello simpleton!
  - I know exactly what you're thinking.
  - You are wondering "Oh Ms. Artiste, how do you make such beautiful pieces?"
  - 'I usually don''t give art tips out to just anyone '
  - '(dont want anyone threatening my art commision business, y''know?) '
  - but I like your hat.
  - It's pointy, and it makes me trust you.
  - You should check out Reddot.com for art tips!
  - That's where I learned EVERYTHING.
